Investment Token Concept:
This Software is designed as an investment token, where funds collected within the smart contract are allocated to generate yield and profits. Any modifications must retain this core concept.

Attribution Requirement:
Any derived work that utilizes, modifies, or redistributes this Software must include an explicit attribution to the original author and acknowledge the core concept of investment token design.

Revenue Sharing Requirement:
If this Software or any derived work generates revenue through yield farming, staking, transaction fees, or any similar mechanism, the entity using this Software is required to transfer 1% of the total generated revenue to the following wallet address:
0x9e787a20B2A328d54F98B63469824eDf0d9FF546
This payment must be made at least once per month.

